    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the Underground Energy Resource Characterization Program to identify the location and characteristics of underground energy resources through the use of slim-hole bores and requires a related environmental assessment or environmental impact statement.  Requires a report to the legislature.  Appropriates funds."
